  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective is to collect skin biopsies rom patients with Costello syndrome to analyze the
      molecular mechanisms responsible for this syndrome caused by a mutation in the HRAS gene and
      the effects of this mutation on energy metabolism and mitochondrial physiology.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
